"{\"uid\": \"salon.com-2024-07-27-chef-kvin-dandrea-on-top-chef-friendships-must-have-ingredients-and-the-summer-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Much like working as a chef in any restaurant kitchen, no matter the caliber or cuisine,\\\"Top Chef\\\"can be a particularly unique and rigorous experience.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chef\", \"from\": 21, \"to\": 27}, {\"ngram\": \"any restaurant kitchen\", \"from\": 31, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"the caliber\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 76}, {\"ngram\": \"cuisine,\\\"Top\", \"from\": 80, \"to\": 92}, {\"ngram\": \"a particularly unique and rigorous experience\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In many cases, a general sense of grit and toughness is the norm, oftentimes calcified after years and years of tense kitchen interactions, incredibly frenzied cooking, frantic moments and immense stressors.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many cases\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 165}, {\"ngram\": \"a general sense\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 182}, {\"ngram\": \"grit\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 190}, {\"ngram\": \"toughness\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 204}, {\"ngram\": \"the norm\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 216}, {\"ngram\": \"oftentimes\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 228}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"tense kitchen interactions\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 290}, {\"ngram\": \"incredibly frenzied cooking\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 319}, {\"ngram\": \"frantic moments\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"immense stressors\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is often shown throughout\\\"Top Chef,\\\" too, particularly during certain challenges, likeRestaurant Wars\\u00c2 or the Mise en Place Race, as well as any moment of the finale cook.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"throughout\\\"Top Chef\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"certain challenges\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"likeRestaurant Wars\\u00c2\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mise en Place Race\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"any moment\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"the finale cook\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Related For Chef Kevin D'Andrea, though, he added a certainje ne sais quoi, if you will \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 nodding to his birthplace \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 oftentimes contributing a sense of levity, a bright smile, a wink and a nod.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chef Kevin D'Andrea\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 570}, {\"ngram\": \"a certainje ne sais quoi\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"his birthplace\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"levity\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"a bright smile\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"a wink\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"a nod\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In both the competition proper and also Last Chance Kitchen, D'Andrea was consistent a bright spot, often adding humor and lightness in a competition show that often times finds itself lacking such ebullience.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both the competition\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"also Last Chance Kitchen\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"D'Andrea\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"a bright spot\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"humor\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"lightness\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"a competition\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"often times\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"such ebullience\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, he made some pretty stupendous dishes, too, combining his culinary background and expertise with his previous experiences on \\\"Top Chef France\\\" to make him quite the well-rounded cheftestant.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 960}, {\"ngram\": \"some pretty stupendous dishes\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"his culinary background\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"expertise\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"his previous experiences\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Top Chef France\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bravo and NBCU must have also been a fan of this energy and have since capitalized on D'Andrea's French heritage, culinary knowledge and on-camera charisma in order to highlight the many athletes competing in the Summer Olympics in Paris: a new Peacock show called \\\"Breaking Baguettes,\\\" hosted by\\u00c2 D'Andrea.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9994325051903331, \"rank\": 0.0005676965019420124, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1386, \"end\": 1391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4066613835914325e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bravo\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"a fan\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"this energy\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1209}, {\"ngram\": \"culinary knowledge\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"camera\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"the many athletes\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"a new Peacock show\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Breaking Baguettes\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As per Eric Goodman withNBC Olympics, \\\"Top Chef\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s charming, whisk-wielding, sports-crazed French cuisine master is inviting U.S. Olympians into his kitchen to get a front row seat to the food of his home nation, France, in the brand new series 'Breaking Baguettes.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French cuisine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\"}, {\"begin\": 1677, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998392177205, \"rank\": 1.570121929400278e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eric Goodman\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"withNBC Olympics\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. Olympians\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"his kitchen\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"a front row seat\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"the food\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"his home nation\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand new series 'Breaking Baguettes\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a fun title clearly a nod to the custom of \\\"breaking bread,\\\" the show slight subverts the custom: As Goodman says, \\\"Inside each [baguette] is a hidden slip of paper \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 fortune cookie style \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 with a spicy question for either Chef Kevin or one of his special guests.\\\"\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 2006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fun title\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1749}, {\"ngram\": \"clearly a nod\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"the custom\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking bread\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1796}, {\"ngram\": \"slight subverts\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"the custom\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"Goodman\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1846}, {\"ngram\": \"baguette\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"a hidden slip\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"paper\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"fortune cookie style\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"a spicy question\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"either Chef Kevin\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1975}, {\"ngram\": \"his special guests\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2004}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can tune into \\\"Breaking Baguettes\\\" now on Peacock or on the NBC Sports YouTube channel.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2071, \"end\": 2081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999690772, \"rank\": 3.0509526629767184e-11, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begi