\"end\": 2340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999999617202783, \"rank\": 3.828006597021302e-08, \"text\": \"Bravo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kevin D\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Andrea\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2303}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Top Chef\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"The following interview\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"clarity\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"length\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hi!\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you do any sort of special preparations for \\\"Top Chef?\\\"\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any sort\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"special preparations\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2463}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Top Chef\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How did your previous \\\"Top Chef\\\" experience aid in your experience?\\u00c2 Yes, absolutely!\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2566, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your previous \\\"Top Chef\\\" experience aid\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"your experience?\\u00c2\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I worked on training myself within the time limits and I also watched other seasons.\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time limits\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"other seasons\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a finalist on Top Chef France, I also was in the unique position to be able to pull from past experience.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.957328692352395e-56, \"text\": \"Top Chef\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\"}, {\"begin\": 2678, \"end\": 2684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998392177205, \"rank\": 1.570121929400278e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a finalist\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2665}, {\"ngram\": \"the unique position\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"past experience\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What would you say is your favorite or best moment of the competition?\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your favorite or best moment\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2812}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Definitely my birthday!\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Definitely my birthday\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It came around while filming and Manny Barella organized a big surprise dinner with the whole family.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Manny Barella\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2904}, {\"ngram\": \"a big surprise dinner\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole family\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a magical moment.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a magical moment\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Was there anything about competing on the show that you did not anticipate?\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Either from the competition standpoint itself, from the television perspective, or perhaps even from watching yourself back after months have passed?\\u00c2 Being in the unique position to have competed on Top Chef internationally, I was likely the most prepared for the style of the show and for watching myself back.\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition standpoint\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3100}, {\"ngram\": \"the television perspective\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"passed?\\u00c2\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"the unique position\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3241}, {\"ngram\": \"Top Chef\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3270}, {\"ngram\": \"the style\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3332}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s always a little out of body to see yourself on screen, but the experience is unlike anything else.\\u00c2 Lots of credit goes to the \\\"Top Chef\\\" team who made us feel comfortable and safe through the duration of filming.\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3382}, {\"ngram\": \"body\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3410}, {\"ngram\": \"screen\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3436}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3456}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3475}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Lots\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3487}, {\"ngram\": \"credit\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3497}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Top Chef\\\" team\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3537}, {\"ngram\": \"the duration\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3584}, {\"ngram\": \"filming\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kevin D'Andrea on \\\"Top Chef\\\" (David Moir/Bravo)Did you have a favorite challenge?\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kevin D'Andrea\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3613}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Top Chef\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"David Moir\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3639}, {\"ngram\": \"a favorite challenge\", \"from\": 3659, \"to\": 3679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Conversely, was there a challenge you really didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t enjoy?\\u00c2 I really enjoyed the chaos challenge \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 that was my favorite!\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 3703, \"to\": 3714}, {\"ngram\": \"the chaos challenge\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t a challenge I specifically didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t enjoy.\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"There wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t a challenge\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even when I was eliminated, I was proud to be leaving after making some of the best risotto they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d experienced on the show.\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best risotto\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 3956}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 3981, \"to\": 3989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Which dish were you proudest of?\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Which dish\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Madison, I made a warm praline chocolate mousse for the duality challenge that I was really proud of.\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4029, \"end\": 4036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.061399563874671e-25, \"text\": \"Madison\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Madison\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a warm praline chocolate mousse\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4076}, {\"ngram\": \"the duality challenge\", \"from\": 4081, \"to\": 4102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had a great feeling about that dish and the feedback from the judges, including Dominique Crenn who was a judge when I came in second on Top Chef France, was really positive.\\u00c2 What was the critique you received during the show that you learned the most from?\\u00c2 \\\"Top Chef\\\" gives you the once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to receive input, advice and support from the judges and renowned chefs.\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4213, \"end\": 4228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominique_Crenn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dominique Crenn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominique_Crenn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominique_Crenn\"}, {\"begin\": 4270, \"end\": 4278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.957328692352395e-56, \"text\": \"Top Chef\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_Chef\"}, {\"begin\": 4279, \"end\": 4285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998392177205, \"rank\": 1.570121929400278e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great feeling\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4152}, {\"ngram\": \"that dish\", \"from\": 4159, \"to\": 4168}, {\"ngram\": \"the feedback\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4185}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 4191, \"to\": 4201}, {\"ngram\": \"a judge\", \"from\": 4237, \"to\": 4244}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 4307, \"to\": 4308}, {\"ngram\": \"the critique\", \"from\": 4318, \"to\": 4330}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 4351, \"to\": 4359}, {\"ngram\": \"the most from?\\u00c2 \\\"Top Chef\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4402}, {\"ngram\": \"a-lifetime\", \"from\": 4426, \"to\": 4436}, {\"ngram\": \"input\", \"from\": 4460, \"to\": 4465}, {\"ngram\": \"advice\", \"from\": 4467, \"to\": 4473}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 4478, \"to\": 4485}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4501}, {\"ngram\": \"renowned chefs\", \"from\": 4506, \"to\": 4520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I tried to take each bit of helpful critique to heart.\\u00c2 Laura Ozyilmaz and Kevin D\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Andrea on \\\"Top Chef\\\" (David Moir/Bravo) Do you have a number-one favorite ingredient to work with?\\u00c2 I cannot exist without garlic and fresh herbs.\", \"from\": 4524, \"to\": 4758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4581, \"end\": 4586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.9922634773134265, \"rank\": 0.007796842191874528, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 4643, \"end\": 4648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999999617202783, \"rank\": 3.828006597021302e-08, \"text\": \"Bravo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each bit\", \"from\": 4540, \"to\": 4548}, {\"ngram\": \"helpful critique\", \"from\": 4552, \"to\": 4568}, {\"ngram\": \"heart\", \"from\": 4572, \"to\": 4577}, {\"ngram\": \"Kevin D\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Andrea\", \"from\": 4599, \"to\": 4615}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Top Chef\", \"from\": 4619, \"to\": 4628}, {\"ngram\": \"a number-one favorite ingredient\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4693}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh herbs\", \"from\": 4743, \"to\": 4754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What stands out for you as a formative moment that got you into cooking or food at large?\\u00c2 When I went to culinary school at 16, my professor, Mr. Troin believed in me, and he was the only one.\", \"from\": 4760, \"to\": 4954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a formative moment\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4805}, {\"ngram\": \"cooking\", \"from\": 4824, \"to\": 4831}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 4835, \"to\": 4839}, {\"ngram\": \"large?\\u00c2\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4850}, {\"ngram\": \"culinary school\", \"from\": 4866, \"to\": 4881}, {\"ngram\": \"my professor\", \"from\": 4889, \"to\": 4901}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr. Troin\", \"from\": 4903, \"to\": 4912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most people, including myself, considered me a lost cause \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 bad at school and completely lost.\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 5051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Most people\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 4966}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 5024, \"to\": 5030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr. Troin helped me understand the love of cooking and the appreciation for focusing on something to become someone in life.\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr. Troin\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5061}, {\"ngram\": \"the love\", \"from\": 5083, \"to\": 5091}, {\"ngram\": \"cooking\", \"from\": 5095, \"to\": 5102}, {\"ngram\": \"the appreciation\", \"from\": 5107, \"to\": 5123}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5140, \"to\": 5149}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 5160, \"to\": 5167}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations on \\\"Breaking Baguettes\\\" (love the name, by the way!)\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Congratulations\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5193}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Breaking Baguettes\", \"from\": 5197, \"to\": 5216}, {\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 5224, \"to\": 5232}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 5237, \"to\": 5244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How did the show come about?\\u00c2 Thank you!\", \"from\": 5247, \"to\": 5288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 5255, \"to\": 5263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking Baguettes is so much fun!\", \"from\": 5289, \"to\": 5323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Breaking Baguettes\", \"from\": 5289, \"to\": 5307}, {\"ngram\": \"so much fun\", \"from\": 5311, \"to\": 5322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a huge fan of sports and especially the Olympics.\", \"from\": 5324, \"to\": 5378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge fan\", \"from\": 5329, \"to\": 5339}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 5343, \"to\": 5349}, {\"ngram\": \"especially the Olympics\", \"from\": 5354, \"to\": 5377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When NBC contacted me about doing this amazing series for the Summer Olympics, I couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t say \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cyes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d fast enough.\\u00c2 Tell me a bit about Foliepops?\", \"from\": 5379, \"to\": 5530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5384, \"end\": 5387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.451104082379023e-16, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this amazing series\", \"from\": 5413, \"to\": 5432}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 5437, \"to\": 5456}, {\"ngram\": \"couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t\", \"from\": 5460, \"to\": 5470}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cyes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 5475, \"to\": 5484}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 5497, \"to\": 5498}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 5507, \"to\": 5512}, {\"ngram\": \"Foliepops\", \"from\": 5519, \"to\": 5528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Foliepop's is a French patisserie located in Austin, Texas where we make delicious pastries \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 particularly the Tartelette.\", \"from\": 5532, \"to\": 5656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5548, \"end\": 5554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9994325051903331, \"rank\": 0.0005676965019420124, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 5577, \"end\": 5590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\", \"score\": 0.9999997186742289, \"rank\": 2.62201748493249e-07, \"text\": \"Austin, Texas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\"}, {\"begin\": 5577, \"end\": 5590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\", \"score\": 0.9999997186742289, \"rank\": 2.62201748493249e-07, \"text\": \"Austin, Texas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_of_the_Americas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Foliepop\", \"from\": 5532, \"to\": 5540}, {\"ngram\": \"delicious pastries\", \"from\": 5605, \"to\": 5623}, {\"ngram\": \"particularly the Tartelette\", \"from\": 5628, \"to\": 5655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Foliepop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Tartelettes are shortbread cookies with creamy fillings and topped with milk, dark or white chocolate.\", \"from\": 5657, \"to\": 5772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tartelettes\", \"from\": 5670, \"to\": 5681}, {\"ngram\": \"shortbread cookies\", \"from\": 5686, \"to\": 5704}, {\"ngram\": \"creamy fillings\", \"from\": 5710, \"to\": 5725}, {\"ngram\": \"milk\", \"from\": 5742, \"to\": 5746}, {\"ngram\": \"dark or white chocolate\", \"from\": 5748, \"to\": 5771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They come in a variety of decadent flavors like: chocolate, lemon, raspberry, peanut, caramel and chai.\", \"from\": 5773, \"to\": 5876, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a variety\", \"from\": 5786, \"to\": 5795}, {\"ngram\": \"decadent flavors\", \"from\": 5799, \"to\": 5815}, {\"ngram\": \"chocolate\", \"from\": 5822, \"to\": 5831}, {\"ngram\": \"lemon\", \"from\": 5833, \"to\": 5838}, {\"ngram\": \"raspberry\", \"from\": 5840, \"to\": 5849}, {\"ngram\": \"peanut\", \"from\": 5851, \"to\": 5857}, {\"ngram\": \"caramel\", \"from\": 5859, \"to\": 5866}, {\"ngram\": \"chai\", \"from\": 5871, \"to\": 5875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Right now, the Foliepop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Tartelettes are available in HEB stores across Central Texas and our goal is to make the Tartelettes available nationwide!\\u00c2 Manuel \\\"Manny\\\" Barella Lopez, Kevin D'Andrea and Tom Colicchio on \\\"Top Chef\\\" (David Moir/Bravo) I am always a sucker for a \\\"Top Chef\\\" friendship and I thought the fun bond you had with Manny was so great and brought such levity to the show.\", \"from\": 5877, \"to\": 6271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5934, \"end\": 5937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H-E-B\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"HEB\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H-E-B\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H-E-B\"}, {\"begin\": 6079, \"end\": 6092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Colicchio\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Colicchio\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Colicchio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Colicchio\"}, {\"begin\": 6119, \"end\": 6124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999999617202783, \"rank\": 3.828006597021302e-08, \"text\": \"Bravo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Foliepop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Tartelettes\", \"from\": 5888, \"to\": 5916}, {\"ngram\": \"Central Texas\", \"from\": 5952, \"to\": 5965}, {\"ngram\": \"our goal\", \"from\": 5970, \"to\": 5978}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tartelettes\", \"from\": 5990, \"to\": 6005}, {\"ngram\": \"Kevin D'Andrea\", \"from\": 6059, \"to\": 6073}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Top Chef\", \"from\": 6095, \"to\": 6104}, {\"ngram\": \"a sucker\", \"from\": 6137, \"to\": 6145}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"Top Chef\\\" friendship\", \"from\": 6150, \"to\": 6173}, {\"ngram\": \"the fun bond\", \"from\": 6188, \"to\": 6200}, {\"ngram\": \"Manny\", \"from\": 6214, \"to\": 6219}, {\"ngram\": \"such levity\", \"from\": 6245, \"to\": 6256}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 6260, \"to\": 6268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What do you think helped the two of you to connect?\", \"from\": 6272, \"to\": 6323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manny is more than a friend \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 he became family.\", \"from\": 6325, \"to\": 6374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Manny\", \"from\": 6325, \"to\": 6330}, {\"ngram\": \"a friend\", \"from\": 6344, \"to\": 6352}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 6367, \"to\": 6373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, I just went to Denver to celebrate his wedding!\", \"from\": 6375, \"to\": 6431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6399, \"end\": 6405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver\", \"score\": 0.9999999997626219, \"rank\": 2.376003252828191e-10, \"text\": \"Denver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 6378, \"to\": 6382}, {\"ngram\": \"his wedding\", \"from\": 6419, \"to\": 6430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When we walked in for the very first episode, Manny was just in front of me in the line to head in.\", \"from\": 6432, \"to\": 6531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the very first episode\", \"from\": 6454, \"to\": 6476}, {\"ngram\": \"Manny\", \"from\": 6478, \"to\": 6483}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 6496, \"to\": 6501}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 6511, \"to\": 6519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We needed to be quiet, but he had his hands behind his back, so I high fived him.\", \"from\": 6532, \"to\": 6613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his hands\", \"from\": 6566, \"to\": 6575}, {\"ngram\": \"his back\", \"from\": 6583, \"to\": 6591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I did, he turned around and smiled.\", \"from\": 6614, \"to\": 6654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I winked back and it was instant friendship.\", \"from\": 6655, \"to\": 6699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"instant friendship\", \"from\": 6680, \"to\": 6698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As we continued to get to know each other, we discovered that we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d been through a lot of similar experiences, including immigrating to the U.S. and working our way up.\\u00c2 What\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s next for you?\", \"from\": 6700, \"to\": 6894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 6762, \"to\": 6768}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 6782, \"to\": 6787}, {\"ngram\": \"similar experiences\", \"from\": 6791, \"to\": 6810}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 6837, \"to\": 6845}, {\"ngram\": \"our way\", \"from\": 6858, \"to\": 6865}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 What\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 6869, \"to\": 6879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am heading home to Paris for the Olympics where some exciting things are in the works!\", \"from\": 6896, \"to\": 6984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6917, \"end\": 6922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4066613835914325e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 6927, \"to\": 6939}, {\"ngram\": \"some exciting things\", \"from\": 6946, \"to\": 6966}, {\"ngram\": \"the works\", \"from\": 6974, \"to\": 6983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hope to share more on that, soon!\", \"from\": 6985, \"to\": 7018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m looking forward to growing the presence and availability of Foliepop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Tartelettes nationwide.\", \"from\": 7020, \"to\": 7127, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 7025, \"to\": 7030}, {\"ngram\": \"the presence\", \"from\": 7058, \"to\": 7070}, {\"ngram\": \"availability\", \"from\": 7075, \"to\": 7087}, {\"ngram\": \"Foliepop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Tartelettes\", \"from\": 7091, \"to\": 7115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more about this topic Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2026 Salon.com, LLC.\", \"from\": 7129, \"to\": 7191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7187, \"end\": 7190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9999999971369107, \"rank\": 2.863382221408765e-09, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this topic\", \"from\": 7145, \"to\": 7155}, {\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2026 Salon.com\", \"from\": 7156, \"to\": 7183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reproduction of material from any Salon pages without written permission is strictly prohibited.\", \"from\": 7192, \"to\": 7288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7226, \"end\": 7231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com